// bootstrap-scenarios.js
// Seeds for synthetic training-data generation.
//
// Each scenario is a starting situation: who the person is acting as,
// what kind of exchange this is, how much weight it carries, and the
// opening line they send. The generator uses this to produce a
// realistic multi-turn dialogue featuring Gabriella, which is then
// parsed into training examples.
//
// Coverage is deliberately wide — the persona-collapse failure mode
// comes from being under-trained on edge cases (phatic greetings,
// simple questions, light exchanges). This library front-loads those
// exact cases so the fine-tune pressures her toward competence there
// specifically.

